description: This Chainlink VRF top 1% rating Yulenka purrs with a rating of 95, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 95, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 5 for East, Box for South, and 1 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80951-45414-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
